376	avalon_20251130_234947	proposal	100100	Charlie	evil	\N	This fits the initial consensus lean: a small, simple first mission with the leader plus one other. Alice is widely trusted as a reasonable starting point, and including myself matches what I already advocated instead of pivoting to a safer-looking choice just to dodge scrutiny. A 2-person team is fully accountable—if there’s a sabotage, both of us come under heavy examination next round, which gives the table concrete info rather than a muddy larger team. While I hear Diana’s concern about me volunteering, I think sticking with the openly discussed pairing is more transparent than suddenly swapping in someone else just because there was pushback.	[-0.02926138,-0.010954209,-0.034626666,-0.044690005,-0.0079031745,0.056706112,0.01574082,0.025277667,-0.03949044,0.07380897,-0.010664074,0.013513597,0.06245724,0.0137350205,0.019998727,0.01953556,0.015591313,0.0070644426,-0.01741208,0.049587965,-0.12604582,-0.18194228,-9.3129776e-05,0.040676914,0.0109452335,-0.009103948,0.009469891,-0.02307538,-0.054250132,-0.08552859,-0.035226505,-0.0054059774,-0.002235492,0.024835395,-0.021781588,0.046496447,0.0339612,0.011177542,0.019490166,-0.028509382,0.011512604,-0.11233187,0.0040797344,-0.07752001,-0.069864646,0.027890649,0.057468116,0.023718262,-0.051850725,-0.05558552,0.02065528,-0.033345573,-0.0058042835,-0.026328877,0.040051978,0.059823375,0.03133083,-0.027772404,-0.0028001072,0.023419425,-0.016705804,0.08802093,-0.031769212,0.02809752,0.019553462,0.007456851,0.002423504,-0.0038250375,0.0025937897,0.046016626,0.0296314,-0.05586024,-0.04563733,-0.13235658,0.0004213165,0.024486538,0.055887166,-0.032784533,0.03272497,0.002303908,-0.035024423,0.021577448,-0.01329626,0.11701023,-0.029637512,-0.08008261,-0.037713196,-0.07693558,0.0100353435,-0.022827957,-0.09416739,0.077213615,0.11200278,0.021193298,0.016970856,0.102044344,-0.0044789356,0.0700497,-0.045380928,0.08411992,-0.0063321455,0.06453585,0.0029052165,-0.043295696,0.0325