428	avalon_20251201_005546	proposal	100400	Eve	good	\N	Mission 1 with Bob and Charlie was clean, and the only fail we’ve seen was when Alice was added to that same pair on Mission 2. That strongly points to Alice as the likeliest source of the fail. Mission 3 was a small, clean 2-person mission, which is helpful but less informative than the 3-player pattern we already have from Missions 1 and 2. By choosing Bob–Charlie–Eve, we avoid the main suspect from the failed mission while relying on the demonstrated compatibility of Bob and Charlie from Mission 1, plus myself, who has only been on clean missions so far. This feels like the lowest-risk configuration given the current information.	[-0.039067578,-0.050875895,0.0030271604,-0.06215994,-0.021232292,0.01816371,-0.028178481,-0.013050567,-0.043009885,0.067375556,-0.0070842225,0.025702743,0.09145162,-0.11307723,0.06396263,0.035952523,0.032230638,-0.02184264,-4.019908e-05,0.0348496,-0.09866942,-0.045179497,-0.0022905946,0.00082106516,-0.0049056425,0.053339355,0.01851981,-0.04823388,-0.03590985,-0.09514413,0.03935467,0.054918725,0.03883177,-0.02576167,0.05072271,0.040657464,0.023071785,-0.023389906,0.011401582,0.012120833,-0.0026498928,-0.031027367,-0.02702811,-0.030904701,-0.058530763,-0.0392973,0.014628308,-0.0070351753,0.051821977,-0.061020114,-0.037666958,-0.042460714,0.004396121,-0.0028061694,0.012972946,-0.058392495,-0.06433838,0.008854826,-0.030755961,0.05758371,-0.046629686,0.05078494,-0.03940829,0.010584149,0.15508787,0.038521487,-0.079144634,-0.099130176,0.013490628,0.0716564,-0.04173028,-0.02371406,-0.115340926,-0.05421177,-0.10857732,0.020427331,0.055134002,-0.007236591,-0.020069739,-0.033825863,-0.0118975425,-0.124732435,0.0070461426,0.069516055,-0.009602457,-0.052273683,-0.08277834,-0.09076948,0.011627465,0.0015326325,-0.020304983,-0.0013341684,0.12890628,0.05780913,0.07075082,0.012223103,-0.015501434,-4.3127857e-05,0.019323366,0.08331729,-0.04599725,0.04631731,0.04069061,-0.061551597,0.083359435,0.0158804